text:
the BEST zi char.

so quick, so yummy. the chilli crab was delicious and perfectly cooked.

our go to zi char in hougang.

dining in or taking out this is the BEST
I ordered a hongkong cao mian to try out. The noodle is soggy (overcooked) and not much ingredients, no veg as well. Taste so so. I don't think it is quality food. You can try.
This neighborhood  zhi char cater mainly for ta pau, take away customer, waited for more than 45 min for a 2 dishes, not worth the waiting time,
